reviews.review_text: Required listening here Yes, it's the Dark Star>Morning Dew I'm talking about. Quality is unexceptional but the incredible power of the music comes through perfectly. Donna's vocals make more sense in audience recordings and lack the abrasive quality of early 70s soundboards.
Not a great ending jam, even if you like '72 shows, and the recording is not that good.
